╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║                 ANALYTICS PROJECT — DESK CHECKLIST (PRINTABLE)              ║
║                         Reusable for Financial Operations                    ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

┌─────────────────────────────────────── Week 1: DISCOVER & DEFINE ───────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Day 1 — Discovery & Kickoff                                                                             │
│ □ Confirm business decision and due date                                                                │
│ □ Draft charter and email to sponsor                                                                    │
│ □ Create folder structure                                                                               │
│ □ Schedule weekly demos                                                                                 │
│ □ Capture initial risks/assumptions                                                                     │
│ □ List data sources and owners                                                                          │
│ ⚠ Red Flag: Day 1 and writing code without a charter                                                    │
│                                                                                                         │
│ Day 2 — Requirements & Mockup                                                                           │
│ □ Build metrics dictionary                                                                              │
│ □ Map data lineage                                                                                       │
│ □ Produce mockup/wireframe                                                                              │
│ □ Review mockup with stakeholders                                                                       │
│ □ Record decision and comments                                                                          │
│ ⚠ Red Flag: Week 2 and stakeholder hasn't seen anything                                                 │
│                                                                                                         │
│ Day 3 — Validation & Plan                                                                               │
│ □ Pull sample data                                                                                      │
│ □ Run quality checks (complete/accurate/consistent/timely/unique)                                       │
│ □ Open validation log                                                                                   │
│ □ Draft analysis plan and estimates                                                                     │
│ □ Lock weekly check-in agenda                                                                           │
│ 🚩 Red Flag: No validation log by Day 3                                                                 │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌──────────────────────────────────────────── Week 2–3: DEVELOP ──────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Every Monday Check-in                                                                                   │
│ □ Demo WIP; capture decisions                                                                           │
│ □ Reconcile metrics vs production                                                                       │
│ □ Update risk/issue log                                                                                 │
│ □ Confirm scope changes + timeline                                                                      │
│                                                                                                         │
│ Build Phase Items                                                                                       │
│ □ Implement iteratively                                                                                 │
│ □ Add docstrings and README updates                                                                     │
│ □ Write unit/spot checks                                                                                │
│ □ Keep decision log current                                                                             │
│                                                                                                         │
│ Red Flags                                                                                               │
│ 🚨 Escalating scope without timeline change                                                             │
│ 🚨 Conflicting numbers without reconciliation plan                                                      │
│ 🚨 No owner for open issues                                                                             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌────────────────────────────────────────────── Week 4: DELIVER ──────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Finalize                                                                                                 │
│ □ Polish visuals, footnotes, units                                                                       │
│ □ Executive summary (BLUF: bottom line up front)                                                         │
│ □ Dry run questions and risk responses                                                                    │
│ Present                                                                                                   │
│ □ Confirm decisions needed and timebox Q&A                                                                │
│ □ Capture action items (owner/date)                                                                       │
│ 🚩 Red Flag: Deliverable format surprises stakeholders                                                   │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌───────────────────────────────────────────── Week 5: DOCUMENT ──────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ □ Lessons learned                                                                                        │
│ □ Update README and metrics dictionary                                                                   │
│ □ Runbook for recurring analyses                                                                         │
│ □ Handoff checklist completed                                                                            │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌────────────────────────────────────── Critical Red Flags — Stop & Reassess ─────────────────────────────┐
│ 🚨 Coding with no charter                                                                                │
│ 🚨 No stakeholder demo by end of Week 1                                                                  │
│ 🚨 Numbers don’t match production with no plan to reconcile                                              │
│ 🚨 Scope change without timeline change                                                                  │
│ 🚨 No owner for data quality issues                                                                      │
│ 🚨 Deliverable format unknown until Week 4                                                               │
│ 🚨 No decision log or action tracking                                                                    │
│ 🚨 No documentation opened by Week 3                                                                     │
└────────────────────
